" Mac Specify================
"map Ctrl + E in normal mode to copy to clipboard
"nnoremap <C-E> "*yy
"map Ctrl + E in visual mode to copy to clipboard
"vnoremap <C-W> "*y
"past clipboard in normal mode, if in visual using CMD+v
"nnoremap <C-D> o<Esc>"*p

"mute the beep sound
set visualbell
set noerrorbells

"auto Center
nmap [ [zz
nmap ] ]zz
nmap G Gzz
nmap { {zz
nmap } }zz
nmap n nzz
nmap N Nzz
nmap L Lzz
nmap H Hzz
nmap g; g;zz
"set in Normal mode
nmap == ==j 
"go to creat a new line below crusor in normal mode
nmap go o<ESC>k
"gO to creat a new line above crusor in normal mode
nmap gO O<ESC>j
nmap K 8k
nmap F 8j
